00:27:01,830 --> 00:27:02,790
Go ahead.

587
00:27:10,850 --> 00:27:12,410
It has green onions, right?

588
00:27:12,680 --> 00:27:13,200
Yes.

589
00:27:15,000 --> 00:27:15,790
I don't eat green onions.

590
00:27:15,790 --> 00:27:16,680
I know.

591
00:27:17,740 --> 00:27:18,400
There's another portion

592
00:27:18,400 --> 00:27:19,660
without green onions.

593
00:27:20,120 --> 00:27:21,560
You made a portion for me too?

594
00:27:21,560 --> 00:27:23,450
Yes. I see you taking care of
the Chief

595
00:27:23,450 --> 00:27:24,910
while juggling your work.

596
00:27:24,920 --> 00:27:25,920
You've lost weight.

597
00:27:25,920 --> 00:27:27,380
So I made a portion for you.

598
00:27:29,920 --> 00:27:30,850
No green onions.

599
00:27:31,870 --> 00:27:32,470
Eat up.

600
00:27:35,190 --> 00:27:35,740
I'll eat then.

601
00:27:35,740 --> 00:27:36,300
Eat.

602
00:27:43,130 --> 00:27:43,720
It's delicious.

603
00:27:43,720 --> 00:27:44,580
Good, isn't it?

604
00:27:47,820 --> 00:27:48,620
Really tasty.

605
00:27:49,560 --> 00:27:50,620
So you can cook too.

606
00:27:50,640 --> 00:27:51,000
Yes.

607
00:27:51,000 --> 00:27:53,400
I like cooking for myself when I'm alone.

608
00:27:53,600 --> 00:27:54,800
I have a big appetite.

609
00:27:55,720 --> 00:27:57,640
I think I didn't make enough.

610
00:28:01,470 --> 00:28:02,730
Mr. Yang, you just said

611
00:28:03,640 --> 00:28:05,100
there are some questions?

612
00:28:05,590 --> 00:28:06,520
What questions?

613
00:28:08,730 --> 00:28:09,530
For you.

614
00:28:14,000 --> 00:28:14,790
A pen for me?

615
00:28:14,790 --> 00:28:17,000
Yes. Actually, your records are fine.

616
00:28:17,240 --> 00:28:19,640
But you need to practice your handwriting.

617
00:28:20,750 --> 00:28:22,880
Whose handwriting should I practice?

618
00:28:26,270 --> 00:28:27,400
Let me show you this.

619
00:28:29,750 --> 00:28:31,720
This is my handwriting.

620
00:28:34,920 --> 00:28:36,510
Actually, my handwriting

621
00:28:37,440 --> 00:28:39,030
can be mistaken for several masters'

622
00:28:39,030 --> 00:28:40,070
calligraphy.

623
00:28:40,510 --> 00:28:41,240
But

624
00:28:41,640 --> 00:28:42,770
I suddenly realized

625
00:28:43,190 --> 00:28:44,590
if I only imitate others,

626
00:28:44,790 --> 00:28:46,160
I would lose myself.

627
00:28:46,480 --> 00:28:47,040
So,

628
00:28:47,440 --> 00:28:48,840
I developed my own style.

629
00:28:49,990 --> 00:28:50,920
That's amazing.

630
00:28:54,510 --> 00:28:55,590
Can I learn from you?

631
00:28:55,590 --> 00:28:56,200
Of course.

632
00:28:56,480 --> 00:28:57,310
Let's eat first,

633
00:28:57,310 --> 00:28:58,110
and after the meal,

634
00:28:58,110 --> 00:28:59,770
we'll practice calligraphy.

635
00:29:03,330 --> 00:29:04,460
Thank you, Mr. Yang.

636
00:29:05,420 --> 00:29:07,620
This is for your calligraphy practice.

637
00:29:24,480 --> 00:29:26,960
I can have the one with green onions.

638
00:29:26,960 --> 00:29:28,090
Let's eat together.

639
00:29:29,550 --> 00:29:30,620
You can cook too?

640
00:29:30,680 --> 00:29:33,090
I live alone and enjoy cooking.

641
00:29:33,200 --> 00:29:34,110
Really?

642
00:29:34,340 --> 00:29:35,140
I should

643
00:29:35,550 --> 00:29:36,750
learn how to cook too,

644
00:29:36,870 --> 00:29:37,930
and learn from you.

645
00:29:59,960 --> 00:30:00,440
Chang.

646
00:30:01,600 --> 00:30:01,990
Yes?

647
00:30:03,360 --> 00:30:04,290
Are you busy now?

648
00:30:04,360 --> 00:30:04,960
Not at all.

649
00:30:05,430 --> 00:30:06,760
Come, let's have a chat.

650
00:30:07,510 --> 00:30:08,790
Sir, please have a seat.

651
00:30:08,790 --> 00:30:09,440
No need.

652
00:30:09,680 --> 00:30:10,510
It's just a few words.

653
00:30:10,510 --> 00:30:10,960
I'll stand.

654
00:30:10,960 --> 00:30:11,480
Please sit down.

655
00:30:11,480 --> 00:30:13,130
If you don't sit, I won't dare to
talk to you.

656
00:30:13,130 --> 00:30:14,060
Please sit down.

657
00:30:17,110 --> 00:30:18,710
Alright, let's sit and talk.

658
00:30:19,210 --> 00:30:20,730
Let me stand. It's fine.

659
00:30:21,140 --> 00:30:23,200
You're standing while talking to me.

660
00:30:24,090 --> 00:30:26,600
What's that supposed to mean?
Want me to look up to you?

661
00:30:26,600 --> 00:30:27,270
No, no.

662
00:30:27,720 --> 00:30:28,720
Sit down and talk.

663
00:30:30,660 --> 00:30:31,520
Comrade Chang,

664
00:30:31,750 --> 00:30:32,310
stand up.

665
00:30:33,180 --> 00:30:34,380
Let's talk standing.

666
00:30:38,200 --> 00:30:39,660
We'll both stand and talk.

667
00:30:41,720 --> 00:30:42,580
It's like this.

668
00:30:43,170 --> 00:30:44,130
Ms. Fang

669
00:30:45,160 --> 00:30:46,960
has told you everything, right?

670
00:30:49,310 --> 00:30:50,880
Yes. She told me.

671
00:30:51,240 --> 00:30:53,890
She said you're extremely busy with work,

672
00:30:54,270 --> 00:30:55,720
and I completely understand.

673
00:30:55,720 --> 00:30:57,720
You're a leader
with countless responsibilities.

674
00:30:57,720 --> 00:30:58,720
That's normal.

675
00:30:58,850 --> 00:30:59,680
Don't worry.

676
00:30:59,810 --> 00:31:02,340
I definitely won't
interfere with your work.

677
00:31:02,550 --> 00:31:05,160
Ms. Fang also said you don't like movies

678
00:31:05,160 --> 00:31:06,690
but prefer symphony music.

679
00:31:07,130 --> 00:31:09,160
I've never listened to symphony music,

680
00:31:09,160 --> 00:31:11,200
but I bought a phonograph and records.

681
00:31:11,200 --> 00:31:12,510
Now I listen every day after work.

682
00:31:12,510 --> 00:31:13,480
I'm learning.

683
00:31:14,310 --> 00:31:16,160
Ms. Fang told you these?

684
00:31:18,270 --> 00:31:19,550
Ms. Fang also said

685
00:31:19,660 --> 00:31:21,220
I'd learn to cook more dishes

686
00:31:21,220 --> 00:31:23,100
to ensure your balanced nutrition

687
00:31:23,100 --> 00:31:25,580
so I can take good care of you.

688
00:31:27,160 --> 00:31:28,880
If Ms. Fang said all that,

689
00:31:29,790 --> 00:31:31,790
I think it's necessary to tell you todayâ€¦

690
00:31:31,790 --> 00:31:32,650
Chang Huijuan,

691
00:31:33,550 --> 00:31:36,270
the patient in bed 16 needs
your nursing care.

692
00:31:37,120 --> 00:31:38,720
Sir, I'll go attend to my duties now.

693
00:31:38,720 --> 00:31:39,640
After I finish my work,

694
00:31:39,640 --> 00:31:42,040
I'll come back to report my thoughts
to you.

695
00:31:58,880 --> 00:31:59,680
Ms. Yi.

696
00:31:59,920 --> 00:32:01,110
Fen's first mother-in-law is here.

697
00:32:01,110 --> 00:32:02,770
I just saw her at the entrance.

698
00:32:03,330 --> 00:32:05,590
What do you mean by first mother-in-law?

699
00:32:06,310 --> 00:32:07,720
Fen is remarried.

700
00:32:07,740 --> 00:32:09,760
So her current mother-in-law
is the second one.

701
00:32:09,760 --> 00:32:10,830
And the first mother-in-law is

702
00:32:10,830 --> 00:32:12,230
from her first marriage.

703
00:32:13,180 --> 00:32:14,510
What nonsense?

704
00:32:16,790 --> 00:32:19,240
Fen's first husband died young.

705
00:32:19,260 --> 00:32:21,510
He died just one month
after they got married.

706
00:32:21,510 --> 00:32:23,180
Fen was a widow for about 7 or 8 years.

707
00:32:23,180 --> 00:32:25,380
She finally found a decent man to marry.

708
00:32:28,030 --> 00:32:28,640
Fen!

709
00:32:29,200 --> 00:32:29,790
Run!

710
00:32:31,030 --> 00:32:32,790
Where's Fen? Fen!

711
00:32:34,880 --> 00:32:36,260
If our fellow villager hadn't told me,

712
00:32:36,260 --> 00:32:37,920
I would've thought you were dead.

713
00:32:37,920 --> 00:32:40,190
I even went to the temple
to pay for blessings for you.

714
00:32:40,190 --> 00:32:43,130
-You went to Shanghai with another man?
-Ms. Tang.

715
00:32:43,800 --> 00:32:44,720
-You shameless bastard!
-Where is Comrade Su?

716
00:32:44,720 --> 00:32:46,320
Comrade Su went to a meeting.

717
00:32:48,200 --> 00:32:49,310
Make them quiet down and sit.

718
00:32:49,310 --> 00:32:50,830
What are you doing? Stop arguing.

719
00:32:50,830 --> 00:32:51,630
Sit down now.

720
00:32:52,000 --> 00:32:53,200
Listen to the leader.

721
00:32:53,550 --> 00:32:54,240
Granny,

722
00:32:54,570 --> 00:32:55,890
let's talk this through calmly.

723
00:32:55,890 --> 00:32:56,720
Who are you?

724
00:32:57,240 --> 00:32:58,770
This is our family business.

725
00:32:58,770 --> 00:32:59,960
It has nothing to do with you.

726
00:32:59,960 --> 00:33:01,880
Fen's marriage is completely legal.

727
00:33:01,880 --> 00:33:03,540
It was approved by the committee.

728
00:33:03,540 --> 00:33:04,460
Enough!

729
00:33:04,510 --> 00:33:06,200
What do you mean by legal?

730
00:33:06,310 --> 00:33:08,000
Fen already has a husband.

731
00:33:08,310 --> 00:33:09,840
She's my daughter-in-law.

732
00:33:10,000 --> 00:33:11,420
She belongs to our family.

733
00:33:11,420 --> 00:33:13,680
Hasn't your son been
dead for 7 or 8 years?

734
00:33:13,890 --> 00:33:15,550
She brought him bad luck
and caused his death!

735
00:33:15,550 --> 00:33:17,610
Don't spread feudal superstitions.

736
00:33:19,790 --> 00:33:21,240
When my son was one year old,

737
00:33:21,240 --> 00:33:22,680
his father died.

738
00:33:23,400 --> 00:33:25,260
I remained a widow my entire life.

739
00:33:25,350 --> 00:33:27,000
You shameless woman,

740
00:33:27,000 --> 00:33:27,880
you couldn't do the same.

741
00:33:27,880 --> 00:33:28,960
She's not you,

742
00:33:29,200 --> 00:33:30,310
nor is she Xiang Lin's wife,
the lamentable widow.

743
00:33:30,310 --> 00:33:31,830
You're Xiang Lin's wife!

744
00:33:31,980 --> 00:33:32,830
You're the unlucky woman!

745
00:33:32,830 --> 00:33:33,790
How dare you push our leader!

746
00:33:33,790 --> 00:33:34,400
Girls, get her!

747
00:33:34,400 --> 00:33:35,320
You shameless.

748
00:33:35,350 --> 00:33:36,440
You shameless.

749
00:33:36,440 --> 00:33:37,920
Get her out of here! Out!

750
00:33:37,920 --> 00:33:38,640
You shameless woman!

751
00:33:38,640 --> 00:33:39,680
Take her out!

752
00:33:45,070 --> 00:33:46,550
Alright, everyone, back to work.

753
00:33:46,550 --> 00:33:48,010
You all go back to work too.

754
00:33:49,090 --> 00:33:49,680
Fen,

755
00:33:50,000 --> 00:33:50,730
are you okay?

756
00:33:53,270 --> 00:33:54,200
Don't be afraid.

757
00:33:54,530 --> 00:33:56,060
You've done nothing wrong.

758
00:34:00,150 --> 00:34:01,110
Ms. Yi.

759
00:34:02,730 --> 00:34:03,460
I'm fine.

760
00:34:06,860 --> 00:34:07,740
Take a rest.

761
00:34:11,550 --> 00:34:12,150
It's okay.

762
00:34:19,730 --> 00:34:20,850
Editor-in-Chief Ji.

763
00:34:20,850 --> 00:34:21,679
Minister Wen.

764
00:34:21,699 --> 00:34:23,370
What a rare visitor you are.
Please sit down.

765
00:34:23,370 --> 00:34:23,900
Alright.

766
00:34:23,909 --> 00:34:24,570
Have a seat.

767
00:34:25,650 --> 00:34:26,989
What brings you to my office?

768
00:34:26,989 --> 00:34:28,030
Here, have some water.

769
00:34:28,030 --> 00:34:28,949
No, well...

770
00:34:29,110 --> 00:34:31,679
Sir, you're just pretending not to know.

771
00:34:31,800 --> 00:34:33,400
Your capable assistant

772
00:34:33,400 --> 00:34:34,590
is coming to our newspaper office.

773
00:34:34,590 --> 00:34:35,510
Don't you know?

774
00:34:41,080 --> 00:34:41,960
Yang Xue'an.

775
00:34:44,920 --> 00:34:46,929
[We hereby send Comrade Yang Xue'an
to work at your office]

776
00:34:46,929 --> 00:34:48,230
He's going to work there?

777
00:34:48,230 --> 00:34:48,880
Yes.

778
00:34:49,070 --> 00:34:50,760
It was arranged by the city leadership.

779
00:34:50,760 --> 00:34:52,489
He'll be working as a reporter.

780
00:34:53,550 --> 00:34:54,360
I see.

781
00:34:55,560 --> 00:34:56,960
What kind of person is he?

782
00:34:57,760 --> 00:34:59,140
He's dedicated and responsible,

783
00:34:59,140 --> 00:35:00,200
highly motivated,

784
00:35:00,710 --> 00:35:02,110
with good writing skill,

785
00:35:02,320 --> 00:35:04,120
and is an excellent young cadre.

786
00:35:04,460 --> 00:35:05,670
That's reassuring.

787
00:35:06,110 --> 00:35:07,400
Now that he's so excellent,

788
00:35:07,400 --> 00:35:09,260
how can you bear to let him go, sir?

789
00:35:09,960 --> 00:35:12,150
Talent needs to circulate.

790
00:35:12,520 --> 00:35:13,450
Don't you agree?

791
00:35:13,920 --> 00:35:15,240
You're highly conscious, sir.

792
00:35:15,240 --> 00:35:16,100
All right then.

793
00:35:16,340 --> 00:35:19,000
When the official transfer order
from the city government arrives,

794
00:35:19,000 --> 00:35:19,920
I'll send it to you.

795
00:35:19,920 --> 00:35:20,590
Good.

796
00:35:20,920 --> 00:35:22,630
I won't take up any more of your time.

797
00:35:22,630 --> 00:35:23,470
I'll be going now.

798
00:35:23,470 --> 00:35:23,950
Leaving already?

799
00:35:23,950 --> 00:35:24,440
Yes, I'm off.

800
00:35:24,440 --> 00:35:25,230
Would you like some water?

801
00:35:25,230 --> 00:35:25,890
No, thanks.

802
00:35:26,110 --> 00:35:27,670
Too much is going on at the newspaper.

803
00:35:27,670 --> 00:35:28,070
All right.

804
00:35:28,070 --> 00:35:28,550
Goodbye, sir.

805
00:35:28,550 --> 00:35:29,400
Welcome to visit me often.

806
00:35:29,400 --> 00:35:30,230
Sure, goodbye!

807
00:35:30,230 --> 00:35:31,090
Okay, goodbye.

808
00:35:38,360 --> 00:35:39,150
He's gone.

809
00:35:42,570 --> 00:35:43,760
Does anyone have any potatoes left?

810
00:35:43,760 --> 00:35:44,710
Give me a potato,

811
00:35:44,840 --> 00:35:46,300
and I'll tell you a secret.

812
00:35:47,590 --> 00:35:48,400
What is it?

813
00:35:50,400 --> 00:35:51,190
Guess what?

814
00:35:51,480 --> 00:35:52,510
Why is Ms. Yi

815
00:35:52,510 --> 00:35:54,110
so worked up about Widow Fen

816
00:35:54,110 --> 00:35:55,030
remarrying?

817
00:35:55,500 --> 00:35:56,230
No idea.

818
00:35:57,000 --> 00:35:59,150
Ms. Yi has been a widow
for several years now.

819
00:35:59,150 --> 00:36:00,800
No less time than Fen.

820
00:36:01,670 --> 00:36:03,840
Who would Ms. Yi fall in love with?

821
00:36:04,030 --> 00:36:05,290
That silver-spoon Fu?

822
00:36:05,590 --> 00:36:07,030
Ms. Su already said it's not him.

823
00:36:07,030 --> 00:36:09,030
Of course it's not silver-spoon Fu.

824
00:36:09,360 --> 00:36:11,000
He is so rich,

825
00:36:11,030 --> 00:36:12,630
and has several concubines.

826
00:36:12,840 --> 00:36:14,920
If he wanted some fun or an affair,

827
00:36:15,030 --> 00:36:16,840
he'd go for a young girl.

828
00:36:17,000 --> 00:36:19,960
What kind of man do you think
Ms. Yi would choose?

829
00:36:20,230 --> 00:36:21,970
She would surely

830
00:36:22,110 --> 00:36:23,710
want another high official.

831
00:36:24,150 --> 00:36:26,320
But if she's now seeing a rickshaw puller

832
00:36:26,320 --> 00:36:27,920
or some laborer, it wouldn't
be surprising.

833
00:36:27,920 --> 00:36:29,520
You know what I mean, sisters?

834
00:36:29,520 --> 00:36:30,410
Yes, indeed.

835
00:36:31,000 --> 00:36:33,150
No wonder I always see her taking

836
00:36:33,180 --> 00:36:35,040
Aniu's rickshaw at the entrance.

837
00:36:35,400 --> 00:36:35,920
You saw that too?

838
00:36:35,920 --> 00:36:37,000
I saw it as well.

839
00:36:37,020 --> 00:36:37,780
Miss Yi Yi.

840
00:36:40,800 --> 00:36:43,730
Seems you're all very interested
in my private life.

841
00:36:45,400 --> 00:36:47,930
I heard you and Fen are
from the same hometown.

842
00:36:48,550 --> 00:36:49,710
Not exactly.

843
00:36:49,710 --> 00:36:51,350
I came to Shanghai very early.

844
00:36:51,350 --> 00:36:52,960
How did Fen's former mother-in-law

845
00:36:52,960 --> 00:36:54,590
know she was here?

846
00:36:55,440 --> 00:36:57,300
Someone must have tipped her off.

847
00:36:57,920 --> 00:36:59,280
What this person's intentions were,

848
00:36:59,280 --> 00:37:00,190
I don't know.

849
00:37:00,710 --> 00:37:02,480
But I can tell you all clearly.

850
00:37:02,840 --> 00:37:04,150
This is the new China.

851
00:37:04,840 --> 00:37:06,720
The old feudal ethics and morals

852
00:37:06,750 --> 00:37:08,010
will surely be buried.

853
00:37:09,230 --> 00:37:10,800
Those with ill intentions

854
00:37:11,590 --> 00:37:13,290
will eventually face the consequences.

855
00:37:13,290 --> 00:37:13,770
I...

856
00:37:13,920 --> 00:37:15,670
I didn't mean that, Ms. Yi.

857
00:37:15,920 --> 00:37:16,360
We...

858
00:37:16,490 --> 00:37:18,300
we all like you very much.

859
00:37:18,480 --> 00:37:20,350
I just gossip.

860
00:37:21,030 --> 00:37:21,880
Ms. Yi,

861
00:37:22,230 --> 00:37:23,690
you're not angry, are you?

862
00:37:24,590 --> 00:37:25,850
Please don't be angry.

863
00:37:26,030 --> 00:37:28,030
You're not going to fire me, are you?

864
00:37:28,590 --> 00:37:30,000
You can't fire me!

865
00:37:30,190 --> 00:37:31,510
I have elderly parents
and young children to support.

866
00:37:31,510 --> 00:37:33,110
If you fire me, what will I do?

867
00:37:33,150 --> 00:37:33,960
Ms. Yi,

868
00:37:34,870 --> 00:37:36,140
if you really fire me,

869
00:37:36,230 --> 00:37:38,000
I'll kill myself right in front of you.

870
00:37:38,000 --> 00:37:39,110
What's all this noise?

871
00:37:39,110 --> 00:37:39,840
Wen Manli,

872
00:37:40,590 --> 00:37:41,440
what nonsense are you talking again?

873
00:37:41,440 --> 00:37:42,510
Try to go die?

874
00:37:42,510 --> 00:37:43,440
Ms. Su.

875
00:37:44,280 --> 00:37:45,280
Get back to work first.

876
00:37:45,280 --> 00:37:47,080
We'll talk after the shift ends.

877
00:37:47,920 --> 00:37:48,510
Stop.

878
00:37:51,320 --> 00:37:52,980
What did you just say about Yi?

879
00:37:54,030 --> 00:37:54,890
I'm asking you.

880
00:37:55,490 --> 00:37:56,230
I... I...

881
00:37:56,230 --> 00:37:57,890
Yi, what did she say about you?

882
00:37:58,070 --> 00:37:58,880
Nothing.

883
00:38:00,150 --> 00:38:01,610
I know your file very well.

884
00:38:02,230 --> 00:38:03,630
I'll deal with you later.

885
00:38:05,590 --> 00:38:06,990
Stop gossiping about Yi.

886
00:38:08,180 --> 00:38:08,740
Let's go.

887
00:38:09,760 --> 00:38:10,800
Alright, alright.

888
00:38:10,800 --> 00:38:12,860
Finish your meal and get back to work.

889
00:38:20,330 --> 00:38:21,590
Hello, Director Fang.

890
00:38:23,360 --> 00:38:24,190
Hello, Director Fang.

891
00:38:24,190 --> 00:38:24,590
Hi.

892
00:38:32,550 --> 00:38:33,350
Minister Wen,

893
00:38:34,030 --> 00:38:35,760
could you come out for a moment?

894
00:38:36,550 --> 00:38:37,360
What is it?

895
00:38:37,360 --> 00:38:38,760
Let's talk in your office.

896
00:38:38,760 --> 00:38:40,110
I'm in a meeting right now.

897
00:38:40,110 --> 00:38:41,030
Just two words.

898
00:38:42,710 --> 00:38:43,110
Go ahead.

899
00:38:43,110 --> 00:38:44,510
Has Old Ji contacted you?

900
00:38:45,570 --> 00:38:47,980
If you don't want Yang to leave,

901
00:38:48,010 --> 00:38:49,940
don't approve his transfer order.

902
00:38:50,440 --> 00:38:52,770
The receiving institution has come to me,

903
00:38:52,960 --> 00:38:54,470
and I knew nothing about it.

904
00:38:54,470 --> 00:38:55,400
Is that normal?

905
00:38:56,550 --> 00:38:58,400
Yang said you told him to leave,

906
00:38:58,890 --> 00:39:01,220
so we naturally assumed you knew about it.

907
00:39:03,440 --> 00:39:04,370
So you're saying

908
00:39:04,880 --> 00:39:05,510
that you

909
00:39:05,760 --> 00:39:07,160
don't want Yang to leave?

910
00:39:07,320 --> 00:39:09,510
Actually, he doesn't want to leave either.

911
00:39:09,510 --> 00:39:11,550
He's just pretending he wants to go,

912
00:39:11,940 --> 00:39:13,600
hoping you'll ask him to stay.

913
00:39:14,640 --> 00:39:16,040
He's overthinking this.

914
00:39:17,360 --> 00:39:18,150
Alright, I understand.

915
00:39:18,150 --> 00:39:19,320
I need to go to a meeting now.

916
00:39:19,320 --> 00:39:20,650
I haven't finished yet.

917
00:39:31,230 --> 00:39:32,320
Why would your factory accept

918
00:39:32,320 --> 00:39:33,610
someone like Wen Manli?

919
00:39:33,610 --> 00:39:35,090
I know her file very well.

920
00:39:35,510 --> 00:39:37,510
She used to be a dancer at Paramount.

921
00:39:38,150 --> 00:39:40,110
She has absolutely no feelings
for the new society.

922
00:39:40,110 --> 00:39:41,840
People like her are just trash.

923
00:39:41,880 --> 00:39:43,100
If we don't take care of her,

924
00:39:43,100 --> 00:39:45,490
her family would end up on the streets.

925
00:39:46,510 --> 00:39:49,240
New China is just established.

926
00:39:49,320 --> 00:39:51,380
We should contribute to our country.

927
00:39:51,510 --> 00:39:53,370
What about her spreading rumors?

928
00:39:53,510 --> 00:39:54,640
Should we deduct her work points

929
00:39:54,640 --> 00:39:55,530
and give her a demerit?

930
00:39:55,530 --> 00:39:57,460
Fine, I'll handle this.

931
00:39:57,490 --> 00:39:58,640
Don't be angry.

932
00:39:58,840 --> 00:40:00,420
You two keep talking. I need to go.

933
00:40:00,420 --> 00:40:01,090
Okay.

934
00:40:03,150 --> 00:40:03,960
Yi.

935
00:40:05,150 --> 00:40:05,880
You

936
00:40:06,510 --> 00:40:07,910
need to be careful of her.

937
00:40:09,030 --> 00:40:10,670
These rumors won't disappear

938
00:40:10,670 --> 00:40:12,070
because you ignore them.

939
00:40:13,150 --> 00:40:14,590
I don't want to waste time and energy

940
00:40:14,590 --> 00:40:15,710
on such matters.

941
00:40:16,000 --> 00:40:17,320
She can't hurt me.

942
00:40:17,400 --> 00:40:18,350
When rumors

943
00:40:18,550 --> 00:40:20,210
are repeated a hundred times,

944
00:40:20,280 --> 00:40:21,810
they will become the truth.

945
00:40:22,920 --> 00:40:24,360
You can't be that naive.

946
00:40:26,590 --> 00:40:27,440
Qing.

947
00:40:28,000 --> 00:40:30,070
You should go now. I need to work.

948
00:40:36,300 --> 00:40:36,920
Yi.

949
00:40:41,880 --> 00:40:42,840
I'm not leaving.

950
00:40:45,360 --> 00:40:46,290
What do you mean?

951
00:40:46,670 --> 00:40:48,600
I want to stay and keep you company.

952
00:40:51,280 --> 00:40:52,540
What's wrong with you?

953
00:40:52,960 --> 00:40:54,630
What do you mean?

954
00:40:54,880 --> 00:40:56,740
You've seen the situation today.

955
00:40:56,880 --> 00:40:58,230
I need to stay by your side
to protect you.

956
00:40:58,230 --> 00:41:00,630
I'm afraid they'll smear your reputation.

957
00:41:01,130 --> 00:41:03,330
Your workplace is far from where I live.

958
00:41:03,460 --> 00:41:04,660
It's not convenient.

959
00:41:05,800 --> 00:41:07,130
What's not convenient?

960
00:41:07,320 --> 00:41:08,960
There are buses.

961
00:41:09,360 --> 00:41:11,630
From now on, I'll come over
after work to keep you company.

962
00:41:11,630 --> 00:41:13,760
We'll keep each other company.
You won't be lonely anymore.

963
00:41:13,760 --> 00:41:14,760
Are you serious?

964
00:41:14,760 --> 00:41:16,320
Of course I'm serious.

965
00:41:18,700 --> 00:41:19,960
What's with that face?

966
00:41:20,190 --> 00:41:21,390
You don't welcome me?

967
00:41:22,550 --> 00:41:24,110
You know what I'm like.

968
00:41:24,410 --> 00:41:25,740
I'm used to being alone.

969
00:41:25,880 --> 00:41:27,610
Not used to living with others.

970
00:41:29,400 --> 00:41:30,110
I...

971
00:41:30,330 --> 00:41:31,460
Am I like the others?

972
00:41:32,150 --> 00:41:33,630
I'm Zhou Zhaoyuan's younger sister.

973
00:41:33,630 --> 00:41:34,670
I'm Zhou Yunqing.

974
00:41:40,590 --> 00:41:41,720
Whose idea was this?

975
00:41:43,110 --> 00:41:44,040
What do you mean?

976
00:41:44,670 --> 00:41:46,070
Are you here to care for me

977
00:41:46,130 --> 00:41:47,340
or to monitor me?

978
00:41:47,370 --> 00:41:49,230
I don't understand what you're saying.

979
00:41:49,230 --> 00:41:51,030
Did Mr. Yang send you to watch me?

980
00:41:52,630 --> 00:41:54,840
Why are you so prejudiced against him?

981
00:41:55,230 --> 00:41:57,360
He wants to protect you and care for you,

982
00:41:57,360 --> 00:41:58,670
afraid others might ruin your reputation.

983
00:41:58,670 --> 00:41:59,670
What reputation?

984
00:42:02,280 --> 00:42:03,280
He just cares about you.

985
00:42:03,280 --> 00:42:04,440
Is he caring about me

986
00:42:04,630 --> 00:42:06,090
or afraid I'll affect you?

987
00:42:06,100 --> 00:42:08,100
What are you saying?

988
00:42:08,550 --> 00:42:10,110
You're being unreasonable!

989
00:42:10,110 --> 00:42:12,190
I don't want you interfering
in my private life.

990
00:42:12,190 --> 00:42:13,110
Is that too much?

991
00:42:13,110 --> 00:42:14,190
Very much so.

992
00:42:14,630 --> 00:42:15,400
Yi Yi.

993
00:42:15,590 --> 00:42:16,880
You're a martyr's widow.

994
00:42:16,880 --> 00:42:18,620
This identity isn't just yours.

995
00:42:18,620 --> 00:42:20,440
You can't disgrace the martyr's name.

996
00:42:20,440 --> 00:42:22,100
You can't be with another man.

997
00:42:22,590 --> 00:42:23,320
Zhou Yunqing!

998
00:42:23,320 --> 00:42:24,070
What?

999
00:42:24,740 --> 00:42:26,530
How can you be so feudalistic?

1000
00:42:26,960 --> 00:42:28,590
Even the factory women
are more progressive than you.

1001
00:42:28,590 --> 00:42:29,440
You're talking nonsense!

1002
00:42:29,440 --> 00:42:30,480
I understand now.

1003
00:42:30,480 --> 00:42:32,030
Go back and tell Mr. Yang.

1004
00:42:32,230 --> 00:42:33,440
Thank him for his good intentions.

1005
00:42:33,440 --> 00:42:35,150
I'll protect my own reputation.

1006
00:42:35,150 --> 00:42:35,840
Also,

1007
00:42:35,880 --> 00:42:37,760
my affairs have nothing to do

1008
00:42:37,760 --> 00:42:38,890
with you or Mr. Yang.

1009
00:42:39,000 --> 00:42:40,030
If you two are worried I'll

1010
00:42:40,030 --> 00:42:41,630
affect your bright futures,

1011
00:42:41,800 --> 00:42:43,930
then distance yourself from me again.

1012
00:42:44,590 --> 00:42:45,440
I won't.

1013
00:42:45,760 --> 00:42:46,800
I'm not leaving.

1014
00:42:47,900 --> 00:42:48,590
You won't leave?

1015
00:42:48,590 --> 00:42:49,190
Yes.

1016
00:42:49,840 --> 00:42:50,570
Then I'll go.

1017
00:42:51,110 --> 00:42:52,450
Don't go.

1018
00:42:53,190 --> 00:42:54,670
If you leave, I'll tear up
your manuscript.

1019
00:42:54,670 --> 00:42:55,870
Tear it up if you want.

1020
00:43:00,280 --> 00:43:01,590
I'm not leaving anyway.
